    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been very well-maintained, offering a reliable and pleasant driving experience. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, and the interior is clean and shows only minor signs of regular use. It serves as a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that has been cared for properly throughout its life.",
